caption:
Meet Taylor, an 18-year-old high school student who loves singing and songwriting. She secretly writes love songs for her crushes and records herself singing it on her phone and then publish it on her top-secret blog.

Until one day, her secret love songs are played over the school PA system, and suddenly Taylor’s love life goes from imaginary to out of control.

blog.description:
Met Taylor 24/06/2015

“So glad you made it tonight, so happy I finally get to meet you!”

summary: “There are lots of places that I always love to explore in Tokyo because you can always find something new and cool and...
body:
“There are lots of places that I always love to explore in Tokyo because you can always find something new and cool and exciting. I’ve been really excited about maybe finding a cat cafe! My friend Ed Sheeran has been to them and told me that they’re basically like, just the best place in the world so… I wanna go and get some ice cream, somewhere with some like colourful cool ice-cream and wanna go to a cat cafe. Do you have any suggestions for where I should go to get really colourful ice cream, or wheres the best cat cafe? It definitely is so exciting to be coming back to Tokyo and I love Tokyo so much that we saved it for last, the last two shows of the tour and I’m so happy to see Tokyo fans. It’s so exciting and I miss you guys so much and thank you for everything!”

— Taylor talking about Japan and coming back to Tokyo in an interview to promote rep Tour Tokyo (x)

blog.name: messofadreamer-13
blog.title: Oh Hey Ben!
blog.description:
Met Taylor 24/06/2015

“So glad you made it tonight, so happy I finally get to meet you!”

summary: “Well this tour is my favourite one that we've done. It’s the most fun I've ever had on tour, and so one of the things I wanted...
body:
“Well this tour is my favourite one that we’ve done. It’s the most fun I’ve ever had on tour, and so one of the things I wanted to do is make sure it was the biggest spectacle we’ve ever put on, the biggest stage I’d ever had. But also have huge moments of spectacle and pyro and a million things go on but then be able to make smaller, more intimate moments where its just me and a guitar or me and a piano and still maintain that connection so its not just a spectacle, but has elements of intimacy too.”

— Taylor talking about the reputation Stadium Tour in an interview promoting rep Tour Tokyo (x)

body:
coming out of the closet

hey guys i just wanted to say that i m bisexual and i hv known it for 4 yrs but never had a courage to come out i still dont i m still freaked out about how u guys will react i think of this as my safe place becoz ppl who i know personally r not on tumblr even if they r i dont know  this is my first step towards me coming out and all i hv to say is that what inspired me is @taylorswift she has been an amazing inspiration the speech that she gave before sang delicate in chicago i wasnt there but i heard the speech and i was inspired by it i want to be myself and not pretend i want to be free and date whoever the hell i want . I want to date without being judged and i know i will take time for me to come out completely to my frnds and family i dont even know if they will support me but i will hv u guys who will and atleast i took a first step and some day i will come out .

Thank u so much for reading this i know u all hv better things to do in life than read me coming out to u guys
